text: Tayyab Abbas (born 6 September 1994) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his List A debut on 14 January 2017 for Rawalpindi in the 2016–17 Regional One Day Cup. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Rawalpindi cricketers Category:People from Attock District
